messageBody:
Everyone:

Rather than bother you nice folks with all my questions, I have created
the new Yahoo! group 'junit-cookbook'. I welcome all attempts to answer
my questions and fuel discussion. Please join us.

I will ask you indulge me by letting me continue to ask questions here,
but refer answerers to the new group. I want to tap the widest possible
network for help. It would be best if you could just all come to Toronto
and help me finish this draft. Work on that.

Thanks so much for your help. See you over there!
--
J. B. Rainsberger,
Diaspar Software Services
http://www.diasparsoftware.com :: +1 416 791-8603
Let's write software that people understand
